high_descs: Move to the brown dresser with a safe on it.
Pick up the credit card on the far right of the dresser.
Move to the left in front of the safe.
Put the credit card inside the safe.
Move back to the right side of the dresser.
Pick up the other blue credit card that is on the dresser.
Move back to the right in front of the safe.
Place the credit card inside.  Shut the door.
Turn around and go across the room to the dresser behind you.
Pick up the credit card that is farther away from you, nearest the back wall.
Turn all the way around to your right, until you are facing the safe on the dresser.
Open the safe, put the credit card in it and close the safe.
Turn to you right, towards the sofa, then fact the dresser on your left.
Pick up the remaining credit card from the dresser.
Turn all the way around until you are facing the safe again.
Open the safe, place the credit card in the safe and close the safe door.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards from the dresser into the safe.

high_descs: Turn right towards the wall, and then turn right to walk towards the dresser.
Pick up the credit card closest to the wall.
Turn to the left of the dresser and open the vault.
Place the credit card inside the vault and close it.
Turn to the right side of the dresser and find the other credit card.
Pick up the credit card from the dresser.
Turn left to find the vault on the dreser.
Place the credit card inside the vault and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place the two credit cards from the dresser into the vault.
